This will be my first IOT project i.e. Arduino based Alcohol breath analyzer .
Purpose of the project is to learn APIs and various IOT components

It will be developed in stages
Result Outputs:-
1- Output will be displayed on 128x128 Pixel OLED Display Module for Arduino
2- Output will be stored in Cloud Google spread sheet
3- Output will be displayed on  Android App and Google spread sheet
4- Output will be emailed to specific people when limit is reached

 Analysis of data
1- Output will maintain a calendar, drinking pattern, Occasion, location,Bar
2-Effects of alcohol on body
3-Cool off times
4-Behavioural change
5-Integrated via App it will start recording talks once activated with higher alcohol limit
6- If too drunk locks Credit card

